column2: select sp.specObjID, sp.objid, so.objid, so.specobjid, sp.mjd, sp.plate, sp.fiberID, sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.z_noqso, sp.zErr_noqso, sp.class, sp.subclass, sp.class_noqso, sp.subclass_noqso, sp.class_person, sp.programme, sp.survey, sp.scienceprimary, zwarning, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak, f.integr, f.rms into mydb.SpecPhoto final from SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN SpecObj as so ON sp.objid = so.objid JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #)
